{
  "_comment": "Comprehensive E2E test workflow for MieLoop — API prompt format.\n\nFour independent loops covering ALL 39 manually-testable MieLoop nodes\n(MieLoopResume is expand-internal and excluded), PLUS disk-offload features.\n\nLoop A (string_list, 4 rounds) — Text/JSON chain + conditions + state int:\n  Start(string), BodyIn, GetIndex, ParamGetString, IfIsFirst/IsLast/CurrentIdx(routed),\n  StateGetInt/SetInt, StringConcat, CollectText, CollectJSON, BodyOut, End,\n  FinalizeTextList, FinalizeJSONList, CleanupText, CleanupJSON, ShowAnything\n\nLoop B (int_range 0..2, 3 rounds) — Image chain + state image:\n  Start(int_range), BodyIn, GetIndex, ParamGetInt, IfIsFirst(routed),\n  StateGetImage, StateSetImage, StateSetImageBatch, StateCleanupImage,\n  CollectImage(offload_to_disk=true, custom dir), ImageSelectFrame, ImageGrid,\n  BodyOut, End, FinalizeImages, CleanupImages, SaveImage\n\nLoop C (json_list, 3 rounds) — Full param/state type coverage + audio offload:\n  Start(json), BodyIn, GetIndex, ParamGetFloat/Bool/String,\n  StateGetFloat/String/Bool, StateSetFloat/String/Bool, StateSet(batch builder),\n  CollectText/JSON, CollectAudio(offload_to_disk=true, custom dir), EmptyAudio, BodyOut, End,\n  FinalizeTextList, FinalizeJSONList, FinalizeAudio, CleanupAudio, ShowAnything\n\nLoop D (int_range 0..11, 12 rounds) — Disk stress: incremental merge (>=10 batches):\n  Start(int_range 0..11), BodyIn, GetIndex, EmptyImage(4x4),\n  CollectImage(offload_to_disk=true, custom dir), BodyOut, End,\n  FinalizeImages(triggers incremental merge with progress log), SaveImage\n\nDisk features tested:\n  - offload_to_disk=true (Image + Audio)\n  - custom offload_dir ('e2e_loop_test/image_offload', 'e2e_loop_test/audio_offload')\n  - .pt cache creation + reload on Finalize\n  - incremental merge (>=10 batches triggers LoopFinalizeMergeProgress log)\n  - .pt cleanup on Finalize success",
  "1": {
